description: This file defines the BookingRepository interface, which extends JpaRepository and provides query methods for BookingEntity objects related to bookings in the airport facility service platform.

classes.name: BookingRepository
classes.description: Repository interface for CRUD operations and custom queries related to BookingEntity objects.

methods.name: findByPassengerIdOrderByCreatedAtDesc
methods.description: Finds all BookingEntity instances for a given passenger ID, ordered by creation date descending.

methods.name: findByPassengerIdAndBookingTypeOrderByCreatedAtDesc
methods.description: Finds all BookingEntity instances for a given passenger ID and booking type, ordered by creation date descending.
